rComments: Doesn't reply to emails. She sits down, hunches over the table and reads off her tablet. I learned more from google than her. Yes, this class was easy, but I gained nothing from it. Complete waste of time and money.

Learning from Dr. Srilata Raman was such a gift. She is a passionate deeply engaging  authentic teacher. I felt so happy to have met such a real teacher who is so scholastic yet also highly approachable. She is very well versed in the material and refined in her wisdom yet is very friendly and open to class discussion and really listens. kind woman
Wonderful professor! Very approachable and helpful. Explains everything very clearly. Assignments are also very straight forward and marked fairly.
Srilata is a very good professor on the whole - she is very intelligent and is good at explaining complicated things.  She sometimes lets student presentations take up too much class time.
